160  break;
161  case TRANSLATE_BACK :
162  quat = tf::createQuaternionMsgFromRollPitchYaw(angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0));
163  start_pose.header.frame_id=END_EFF_FRAME;
164  start_pose.pose.position.x=0;
165  start_pose.pose.position.y=0;
166  start_pose.pose.position.z=-distance;
167  start_pose.pose.orientation = quat;
168  break;
169  case TRANSLATE_FRONT :
170  quat = tf::createQuaternionMsgFromRollPitchYaw(angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0));
171  start_pose.header.frame_id=END_EFF_FRAME;
172  start_pose.pose.position.x=0;

187 geometry_msgs::TwistStamped getTwistForDirection(int direction)
188 {
189  geometry_msgs::TwistStamped twist;
190  twist.header.stamp=ros::Time::now();
191  twist.header.frame_id="j2s7s300_link_7";
192  switch(direction)
193  {
194  case ARC_DOWN:
195  ROS_INFO("Arc down");
196  twist.twist.linear.z=VEL_LIN_MAX;
197  twist.twist.angular.x=VEL_ANG_MAX;
198  break;
199 
200  case ARC_UP:
201  ROS_INFO("Arc up");
202  twist.twist.linear.z=-VEL_LIN_MAX;
203  twist.twist.angular.x=-VEL_ANG_MAX;
204  break;
205 
206  case TRANSLATE_BACK:
207  ROS_INFO("Translate back");
208  twist.twist.linear.x=-VEL_LIN_MAX;
209  break;
210 
211  case RAISE_CUP:
212  ROS_INFO("Raise Cup");
213  twist.twist.angular.x=VEL_ANG_MAX;
214  break;
215 
216  case LOWER_CUP:
217  ROS_INFO("Lower Cup");
218  twist.twist.angular.x=-VEL_ANG_MAX;
219  break;
220 
221  case TRANSLATE_UP:
222  ROS_INFO("Translate up");
223  twist.twist.linear.z=VEL_LIN_MAX;
224  break;
225 
226  case TRANSLATE_DOWN:
227  ROS_INFO("Translate down");
228  twist.twist.linear.z=-VEL_LIN_MAX;
229  break;
230 
231  }
232  return twist;
233 }

349 void driveToRollGoalWithVelocity(int direction)
350 {
351  if(direction == RAISE_CUP)
352  ROS_INFO_STREAM("Raise cup");
353  else if (direction == LOWER_CUP)
354  ROS_INFO_STREAM("Lower cup");
355  else
356  {
357  ROS_ERROR_STREAM("Wrong direction given!!");
358  return;
359  }
360 
361  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped start_pose, goal_pose, temp_pose;
362 
363  lock_pose.lock();
364  start_pose=current_pose;
365  lock_pose.unlock();
366 
367  double temp_rol, temp_pit, temp_yaw;
368  double goal_rol, goal_pit, goal_yaw;
369  double start_rol, start_pit, start_yaw;
370  double del_rol;
371 
372  goal_pose = start_pose;
373 
375  tf::Quaternion q_rot = tf::createQuaternionFromRPY(angles::from_degrees( direction==RAISE_CUP?rotation_step:-rotation_step),angles::from_degrees(0),angles::from_degrees(0)); // Rotate about x by 20 degrees
376  tf::Quaternion q_start; tf::quaternionMsgToTF(start_pose.pose.orientation, q_start);
378  tf::Quaternion q_goal = q_start*q_rot;
379 
381  tf::quaternionTFToMsg(q_goal,goal_pose.pose.orientation);
382 
384  ros::Rate loop_rate(100);
385  //ros::Time start = ros::Time::now();
386  while(ros::ok())
387  {
388  lock_pose.lock();
389  temp_pose = current_pose;
390  lock_pose.unlock();
391 
392  getRPYFromQuaternionMSG(goal_pose.pose.orientation, goal_rol, goal_pit, goal_yaw);
393  getRPYFromQuaternionMSG(temp_pose.pose.orientation, temp_rol, temp_pit, temp_yaw);
394  getRPYFromQuaternionMSG(start_pose.pose.orientation, start_rol, start_pit, start_yaw);
395 
397  if (goal_rol < 0 ) goal_rol = goal_rol + angles::from_degrees(360);
398  if (temp_rol < 0 ) temp_rol = temp_rol + angles::from_degrees(360);
399 
400  del_rol = goal_rol - temp_rol;
401 
402  if (std::fabs(del_rol)>=thresh_ang)
403  {
404  float linear_vel = 0.02;
405  geometry_msgs::TwistStamped twist_msg;
406  twist_msg.twist.linear.x = 0;
407  twist_msg.twist.linear.y = 0;
408  // Comment out next line ONLY if using end-effector mode ie: Mode 1 on jostick is active and 4th blue LED on far right is active.
409 // twist_msg.twist.linear.z = direction==RAISE_CUP ? linear_vel : -linear_vel;
410  twist_msg.twist.angular.x= del_rol>0?VEL_ANG_MAX:-VEL_ANG_MAX;
411  twist_msg.twist.angular.y = 0;
412  twist_msg.twist.angular.z= 0;
413 
414  if(isForceSafe() && isAudioSafe())
415  {
416  cmd_vel.publish(twist_msg);
417  }
418  else
419  {
420  ROS_WARN("ABORTING SEQUENCE!!!");
421  fallback(true);
422  ros::shutdown();
423  }
424  }
425  else
426  {
427  //ROS_INFO_STREAM("Goal reached, breaking loop");
428  break;
429  }
430 
431  ros::spinOnce();
432  loop_rate.sleep();
433  }

581 void callFallbackTimer(double duration)
582 {
583 
584  ros::Time start = ros::Time::now();
585  ros::Duration run_for(duration);
586  ros::Rate loop_rate(10);
587  ROS_WARN_STREAM("Starting fallback timeout for: " << duration << "s.");
588  while(ros::Time::now() - start <= run_for)
589  {
590  lock_force.lock();
591  double force = force_f;
592  lock_force.unlock();
593

596  ROS_INFO_STREAM("Force detected, breaking out of timer");
597  return;
598  }
599 
600  loop_rate.sleep();
601  ros::spinOnce();
602  }
603 
604  ROS_WARN_STREAM("Time out! Initialising fallback");
605  // moveCup(TRANSLATE_BACK);
606  fallback();
607  sleep(1);
608  ros::shutdown();
609 }

611 void fallback(bool emerg)
612 {
613  lock_pose.lock();
614  geometry_msgs::PoseStamped start_pose=current_pose;
615  lock_pose.unlock();
616 
617  double roll, pitch, yaw;
618  getRPYFromQuaternionMSG(start_pose.pose.orientation, roll, pitch, yaw);
619 
620  int yaw_degrees = angles::to_degrees(yaw);
621 
622  // ROS_INFO_STREAM("Current yaw float: " << angles::to_degrees(yaw) << " int " << yaw_degrees);
623 
624  geometry_msgs::TwistStamped twist_cmd;
625 
631  // y = mx + c
632  double m = 0.004444444;
633  double velx_c = 0.8;
634  double vely_c = 0.4;
635 
636 
642 
643  if (yaw_degrees >= -180 && yaw_degrees < -90)
644  {
645  //ROS_INFO_STREAM("Sector 1");
646  twist_cmd.twist.linear.x = m * yaw_degrees + velx_c;
647  twist_cmd.twist.linear.y = m * yaw_degrees + vely_c;
648  }
649  else if (yaw_degrees >= -90 && yaw_degrees <0)
650  {
651  //ROS_INFO_STREAM("Sector 2");
652  twist_cmd.twist.linear.x = -m * yaw_degrees;
653  twist_cmd.twist.linear.y = m * yaw_degrees + vely_c;
654  }
655  else if (yaw_degrees >= 0 && yaw_degrees <90)
656  {
657  //ROS_INFO_STREAM("Sector 3");
658  twist_cmd.twist.linear.x = -m * yaw_degrees;
659  twist_cmd.twist.linear.y = -m * yaw_degrees + vely_c;
660  }
661  else if (yaw_degrees >= 90 && yaw_degrees <=180)
662  {
663  //ROS_INFO_STREAM("Sector 4");
664  twist_cmd.twist.linear.x = m * yaw_degrees - velx_c;
665  twist_cmd.twist.linear.y = -m * yaw_degrees + vely_c;
666  }
667  //ROS_INFO_STREAM("Publishing twist : ");
668  //std::cout << (twist_cmd) << std::endl;
669  if (emerg==true) twist_cmd.twist.angular.x = -1;
670  publishTwistForDuration(twist_cmd,1);
671 }

694 std::vector<std::vector<std::string> > CSVReader::getData()
695 {
696  std::ifstream file(fileName);
697 
698  std::vector<std::vector<std::string> > dataList;
699 
700  std::string line = "";
701  // Iterate through each line and split the content using delimeter
702  while (getline(file, line))
703  {
704  std::vector<std::string> vec;
705  boost::algorithm::split(vec, line, boost::is_any_of(delimeter));
706  dataList.push_back(vec);
707  }
708  // Close the File
709  file.close();
710 
711  return dataList;
712 }

748 int calculateCurrentState(double force, int step)
749 {
750  int force_state;
751 
752  if (force >= 0 && force < FORCE_F_1_2_THRESH) force_state = 0;
753  else if (force >= FORCE_F_1_2_THRESH && force < FORCE_F_2_3_THRESH) force_state = 1;
754  else force_state = 2;
755 
756  int current_state = (3 * step) + force_state;
757 
758  return current_state;
759 }
